  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mi>y</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>8</mn></math></p>\n<p>Which of the following consists of the <em>y</em>-coordinates of all the points that satisfy the system of inequalities above?</p>",
