  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Subtracting 2 from both sides of 3x > 8 yields 3x - 2 > 6. Combined with y > 3x - 2, by transitivity y > 6. Choice A solves only for x. Choice B uses the wrong constant. Choice C is incorrect.</p>",
